研究数据表明，有过敏性哮喘的患者同时合并过敏性鼻炎的比例达到80%，反过来说，有季节性过敏性鼻炎的患者合并有过敏性哮喘的，达到了40%。”雷暴加哮喘，你的鼻子会经历什么_新闻频道_中国青年网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IwY+M9uSsjes2EAMaCTEwMDM4OTc0NiCnpvunBjAAOERAHXIJNjIxNDk1MTUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"4.2 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-28e3bf554d6cf326c0186808867b9ce2_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"30_1694740326.703033","card_id":"Q_621982479","target":{"id":621982479,"title":"有哪些诗句是描述秋天的？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/621982479","type":"question","created":1694656102,"answer_count":114,"follower_count":154,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[17884,29154,313205],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIwY+M9uSsjes2EAMaCTEwMDQ5Nzk2MSDmzImoBjAAOJoBQB5yCTYyMTk4MjQ3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"4.2 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1694740326.704127","card_id":"Q_621098169","target":{"id":621098169,"title":"统计专业大一新生，不懂为什么大伙都推荐得学R语言?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/621098169","type":"question","created":1694164700,"answer_count":19,"follower_count":82,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[41413,87589,199757],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"这个语言平时也没听说过，它在统计方面有什么特殊的地方吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IwY+M9uSsjes2EAMaCTEwMDMwMTUzOCDczeunBjAAOFJAH3IJNjIxMDk4MTY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"4.2 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1694740326.705261","card_id":"Q_621683978","target":{"id":621683978,"title":"湖北特校性侵案代理律师自曝阅卷遭法院羁押